\v 4 \w Now|strong="H2009"\w* \w at|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* very moment, \w Boaz|strong="H1162"\w* arrived \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w Bethlehem|strong="H1035"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w greeted|strong="H1288"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* harvesters, “\w May|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*\nd* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w you|strong="H5973"\w*!” \w They|strong="H3068"\w* replied, “\w May|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*\nd* \w bless|strong="H1288"\w* \w you|strong="H5973"\w*!”
\v 5 \w Boaz|strong="H1162"\w* asked \w his|strong="H5921"\w* \w servant|strong="H5288"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w charge|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* harvesters, “\w To|strong="H5921"\w* \w whom|strong="H4310"\w* does \w this|strong="H2063"\w* \w young|strong="H5288"\w* \w woman|strong="H5291"\w* belong?”
